{
  "stem": "7624.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we had-- we put two boys, two boys in each compartment.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were [? in a ship. ?] I was with a very good friend of mine who is still alive in Paris.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were close friends.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On a train-- and we were inspected by the German [GERMAN SPEECH] army.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The [GERMAN SPEECH] army, they had the metal things there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were very tough guys.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, my papers, I had a very strong German accent.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my paper says I came from [INAUDIBLE], which is they speak German and French.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So it was OK.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I remember I was blonde, blue eyes, didn't look Jewish at all.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they inspect my papers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I didn't have no problem, my friend either.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But the next, next compartment, we had a couple of boys.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I don't know if there paper was not so good or what had happened, but I found out that they were not pleased with their papers.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they asked the boys to take their pants off.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On the train-- when he saw that the boys were circumcised, they grabbed them, put--",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Handcuffs on them-- and I still saw them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was in Montauban, France, where they got him and took him out the train.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I saw him the last time from those boys.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Anyway, we came to a place where we supposed to meet some other boys and to get over the Spanish border.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When we got there, everybody was gone, because there was a rifle.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The German came there already before.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But everybody was-- they found out that somebody is-- the Germans going to come.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So they all went away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Then I found out that we shouldn't go to Spain, because the Spain, they won't let you go through.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
